@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Create Branch button;
|System|
: (2) Display form to create new Branch;
|User|
repeat : (3) Input Branch Information;
: (4) Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: (5) Validate Branch Information;
backward: (6) Show error message;
repeat while (Information Valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: (7) Add branch information to database;
: (8) Update Manage Branch screen;
stop
@enduml